sudo -i ---> mkdir masthan 
cd / ---> chown jenkins:jenkins /root/ (Do ec2-user)
chown jenkins:jenkins /root/masthan (Do root-user)
job ---> configur ---> advanced ---> USE CUSTOM WORKSPACE ---> /root/masthan ---> save & build.

Note:
 1. give jenkins permissions for root user & group. (Do ec2-user)
    ex: dr-xr-x---   5 jenkins jenkins  161 Jan 12 06:59 root

 2. give jenkins permissions for masthan(normal) user & group. (Do root user)
    ex: drwxr-xr-x 2 jenkins jenkins   6 Jan 12 06:53 masthan

    
